snippet.title: Gallop Racer 2 Arcade
snippet.description:
The fast-paced arcade style racing Tecmo Series returns.
Gallop Racer 2 will not only appeal to the racing enthusiast, but also to more casual gamers due to its easy accessibility.
Be the jockey whose career depends on every race.
